data.description:
Welcome to this gorgeous custom ranch-style home, nestled on 5.57 acres of serene and private land. The property offers an oasis of tranquility, and privacy. With its huge oversized windows, the home effortlessly brings the outdoors in, allowing you to immerse yourself in the panoramic views that surround you. The spacious custom floor plan, offering 2916 sq ft, is to designed to provide both comfort and functionality. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there's plenty of room for family and guests. The large kitchen is a true centerpiece, perfect for entertaining. Throughout the home, exquisite craftsmanship is evident, adding an
extra touch of elegance and sophistication.
